text: iPad (6th generation), also known as iPad (2018), is a tablet that was made by Apple and released in 2018. ==Features== ===Display=== It has a display. ===Cameras=== It has an 8 MP rear and 1.2 MP front cameras. The rear camera is in operation at f2.4 aperture. ===Performance=== It has an A10 Fusion processor and 2 GB RAM. ===Software=== It first supplied with iOS 11.3. It now supports iPadOS 15.3.1.
